text.section:
Ex officio membership of the Advisory Committee shall include:
The Secretary of Business and Economic Development, or the Secretary's designee;
The Secretary of the Environment, or the Secretary's designee;
The Secretary of Natural Resources, or the Secretary's designee;
The Director of the Maryland Energy Administration, or the Director's designee; and
The Dean of the College of Agriculture and Natural Resources at the University of Maryland, or the Dean's designee.
